p3Content1: At Dont Fret, we believe that everyone should have access to high-quality musical instruments. That's why we offer our handmade creations at affordable prices without compromising on the quality or craftsmanship. You can trust us to deliver exceptional value for your investment.

contactBlurb: If you are interested at all in any of the services I provide, get in contact with us and we will do our best to help you out.
supportingHeading: At Dont Fret, we take pride in creating unique, handcrafted musical instruments that are tailored to your specific needs and preferences. Jade's expertise as an amateur luthier ensures that each instrument is crafted with meticulous attention to detail and precision.

secondaryContent: Whether you're a seasoned musician or just starting out, we offer a diverse selection of handmade instruments including guitars, ukuleles, violins, and more. Each instrument is carefully crafted using the finest materials to produce exceptional sound quality.
titleContent: Crafting harmony, one string at a time.
